試驗她一下面對誘惑，她就會毫不猶豫的拋棄你。<br />\n<br />\n寧可娶婊做某，不可娶某做婊<br />\n<br />\n就算她在婚前如何淫亂，只要過門入室當老婆後安分守己，總比那些婚前安分守己， 但婚後淫亂濫好太多。<br />\n<br />\n在這種情況設定之下，經計算後天生麗質的女有較大機會性格閪，係一個閪人，與此同時，佢哋都有較大嘅本錢咁做。<br />\n<br />\n得出結論，天下烏鴉一樣黑，好女難尋⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n最後送上詩句<br />\n<br />\n煙花妓女俏梳妝，<br />\n洞房夜夜換新郎，<br />\n一雙玉腕千人枕，<br />\n半點朱唇萬客嘗，<br />\n裝就幾般嬌羞態，<br />\n做成一片假心腸，<br />\n迎新送舊知多少，<br />\n故落嬌羞淚兩行。<br />\n<br />\n最後留下一個問題，大家在測度人心嘅同時，是否和閪婊的考量，在本質上沒有分別？</blockquote><br />\n</del><br />\n做咩啫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bd5019c96f9a88a705a5148183b3281a2382bc","tid":369851,"uid":1374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"到現實咪又係個個都揀靚個個<br />\n問黎都晒氣"},{"pid":"b0717d33c526a9e91876f95aabbbf2ddb9bccefc","tid":369851,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"揀大波嗰個"},{"pid":"4faf87243b478eabbbd9c5447f8b41f65c11c54e","tid":369851,"uid":121053,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"揀大波靚 性格好個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9102af3202b23559b357336f1a6cfac072761e9","tid":369851,"uid":33991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"根本樓主以為自己係後者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36af582e394f786bdc0953cc9cb408e175a8f031","tid":369851,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"唔好個個都話醜就算"},{"pid":"445cf09fd60fe7f17565c1bb0dc76ca868a47653","tid":369851,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"大把絲打負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec6cc1ae5be92d127e2cab3e35d10b62b9cb2bf","tid":369851,"uid":11428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20